    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">From application to first engagement.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 26px;max-width:70ch;">Four phases. Typical timeline three to six weeks. Application is free; no obligation at any stage.</p>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-step__n">PHASE 1</div>
        <h3>Apply</h3>
        <p>Submit the application with credentials, practice details, capacity, geographic coverage, and any specializations. Takes about 20 minutes &mdash; <strong>free, no obligation</strong>.</p>
