        <div class="process-step__n">PHASE 2</div>
        <h3>Fit Call</h3>
        <p>30-minute call to discuss the model, mutual expectations, and what your practice is looking for. Both sides decide whether to continue &mdash; <strong>typically within 1&ndash;2 weeks</strong>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-step__n">PHASE 3</div>
        <h3>Verification</h3>
        <p>Credential verification, insurance review, reference checks, and a brief work-sample discussion. Standard for every operator &mdash; <strong>typically 1&ndash;2 weeks</strong>.</p>
