        <div class="process-step__n process-step__n--done">PHASE 4 &check;</div>
        <h3>Onboarding</h3>
        <p>Operator agreement signed. Onboarding to TechBrot&rsquo;s tooling, quality standards, intake workflow, and engagement routing. First engagement scoped within weeks &mdash; <strong>typically 1&ndash;2 weeks</strong>.</p>
      </div>
